			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<note>[Überschrift:]</note>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Joach[imus] Vadianus</persName>, tertio Calend. Febr. 1547.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8011" cert="high">Gwaltheri</persName> rebus vellem abs te mature et bona fide certior fieri.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nil dubita, quin omnia illius caussae suae hoc peius apud adversarios habeant, quod <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4091" cert="high">Zvinglii</persName> nostri gener est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quam facile autem opprimentur, si tacere nos ad quamlibet maledicas calumnias iniuriasque, papae<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p19981" cert="high">Paul III.</persName></note> imprimis, nihil reponere et fidei nostrae rationem reddere orbi iudicanti non licebit!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eritne salva conductio foederis, quae et nostrae nos religioni asserit?</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wie werden wir bey unserem glauben bleiben mögen, wann sy uns denselbigen gegen den lesterer zu vertedigen und allen spann an den tag zu thun nicht zulassen wollen?</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed id genus artes promovent episcopi et abbates clanculariis suis in conventiculis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="signature">[Ohne Unterschrift.]</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
